3 Data overview

There are a total of 30549 rows in this final dataset of which , 11285 have all the information annotated and 19264 are missing SMILES.
This represents a fail rate of 63.1 % .

There are 6573 unique CAS identified compounds in this dataset across 14 groups. Some groups have fewer than 50 compounds entered, which will be removed.
